message:
Fix issues of:
            Follow symlink flag is not passed to enumerator.
            PreserveSMBAttributes test cases should not run on non-Windows platform.

added: var fileEnumerator = new FileHierarchyEnumerator(this.source as DirectoryLocation, this.baseDirectoryTransfer.Source.Instance as string, this.baseDirectoryTransfer.FollowSymblink);
deleted: var fileEnumerator = new FileHierarchyEnumerator(this.source as DirectoryLocation, this.baseDirectoryTransfer.Source.Instance as string, false);
